Body: Description: Server unavailable after applying the latest FW. Please advise.
I reached out to DevOps directly and the revert to snapshot requested by the customer was performed yesterday, 18/12/2024 approximately 1 hour after the customer's follow up.
Postponing reply as we are still waiting on an answer from R&D to send to customer

What We've Learned Updated: the server was not accessible due to the first bug with patch 5.9.4.1
since then the server was rolled back to a state before the patch
Next Steps Updated: waiting for the server to be generally available and update the server
